        <mxCell id="flow-steps" value="1. Firestore document update triggers Cloud Function&#xa;2. Function reads before/after status snapshots&#xa;3. Determines notification type from status transition&#xa;4. Resolves recipient fcmTokens[] from users collection&#xa;5. Applies filters (quiet hours, self-exclusion)&#xa;6. Selects custom sound for notification channel&#xa;7. Sends via FCM v1 HTTP API&#xa;8. Mobile app receives + plays sound + shows alert" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=#555;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
